        <?php echo $this->stencil->setHeadline('Mustache Template System'); ?>
        <p><strong>Mustache</strong> is a simple web template system with implementations available for <?php echo $this->stencil->addLink('ActionScript', 'L'); ?>, <?php echo $this->stencil->addLink('C++', 'LC'); ?>, <?php echo $this->stencil->addLink('Clojure', 'L'); ?>, <?php echo $this->stencil->addLink('CoffeScript', 'L'); ?>, <?php echo $this->stencil->addLink('ColdFusion', 'L'); ?>, D, <?php echo $this->stencil->addLink('Erlang', 'L'); ?>, Fantom, <?php echo $this->stencil->addLink('Go', 'L'); ?>, <?php echo $this->stencil->addLink('Java', 'L'); ?>, <?php echo $this->stencil->addLink('JavaScript', 'L'); ?>, Lua, <?php echo $this->stencil->addLink('.Net', 'L'); ?>, <?php echo $this->stencil->addLink('C', 'L'); ?>, <?php echo $this->stencil->addLink('Perl', 'L'); ?>, <?php echo $this->stencil->addLink('PHP', 'L'); ?>, <?php echo $this->stencil->addLink('Python', 'L'); ?>, <?php echo $this->stencil->addLink('Ruby', 'L'); ?>, <?php echo $this->stencil->addLink('Scala', 'L'); ?> and XQuery.</p>
        <p>Mustache is described as a "<strong>logic less</strong>" system because it lacks any explicit control flow statements, like <code>if</code> and <code>else</code> conditionals or for loops; however, both looping and conditional evaluation can be achieved using section tags processing lists and lambdas.</p>
        <p>It is named "Mustache" because of heavy use of curly braces that resemble a mustache.</p>
        <p>Official Mustache Template System website: <?php echo $this->stencil->addExternalLink('mustache.github.io', 'http://mustache.github.io/'); ?></p>
